WEBVTT

01:37.020 --> 01:40.970
[The Best Thing]

01:41.340 --> 01:45.500
[Episode 4: Mint;
Pungent, cool, dispels wind-heat, clears head and eyes, soothes throat, promotes rashes, and regulates liver qi]

01:46.430 --> 01:46.870
Okay.

01:47.280 --> 01:48.640
As long as it's your prescription.

01:49.350 --> 01:51.400
I'll pack the donkey-hide gelatin for her separately.

01:51.750 --> 01:52.580
One week's dosage.

01:53.880 --> 01:54.910
Okay, no problem.

01:54.950 --> 01:55.840
Then that's it for now.

01:57.640 --> 01:59.070
I've confirmed it. It's all good.

01:59.370 --> 02:00.700
Please come to pick it up in four hours.

02:00.730 --> 02:02.040
Okay, thank you.

02:02.950 --> 02:03.510
See you.

02:03.510 --> 02:03.920
See you.

02:10.009 --> 02:10.710
Ms. Wu.

02:11.430 --> 02:12.030
What's up?

02:12.800 --> 02:14.150
Was that Miss Shen? She came again?

02:14.150 --> 02:15.080
What's wrong?

02:16.520 --> 02:18.190
Dr. He asked me for her phone number.

02:18.750 --> 02:19.430
Really?

02:20.030 --> 02:21.000
I didn't even notice that.

02:21.000 --> 02:22.150
Shh, keep it down...

02:22.150 --> 02:23.800
Tell me the story.

02:34.280 --> 02:36.840
Feel the energy of nature.

02:36.840 --> 02:38.840
Perilla leaves.

02:39.300 --> 02:40.500
I'm craving barbecue.

02:59.400 --> 03:01.360
Nice handwriting, Dr. He.

03:09.750 --> 03:11.190
This medicine's way too bitter.

03:12.030 --> 03:13.680
What does it include this time?

03:14.780 --> 03:16.220
It literally starts with the bitter goldthread.

03:17.310 --> 03:18.870
Let me check the components.

03:21.550 --> 03:23.360
Fried Atractylodes macrocephala...

03:23.380 --> 03:24.220
What is it?

03:29.150 --> 03:30.310
It appears dark brown...

03:30.310 --> 03:31.630
Gosh, I can tell it's bitter just by looking at it.

03:35.360 --> 03:36.840
Tree peony bark...

03:50.280 --> 03:51.120
What else is in there?

03:56.610 --> 03:57.680
Why are you still up at this hour?

03:58.280 --> 03:59.190
Suffering from insomnia?

04:08.360 --> 04:10.290
I'm about to hit the hay.

04:15.310 --> 04:16.829
Stop scrolling on your phone before bed.

04:17.190 --> 04:19.310
Ease your mind. It helps with sleep.

04:20.160 --> 04:21.240
I saw your Moments.

04:22.730 --> 04:24.240
You're not asleep either.

04:28.920 --> 04:31.800
How can I reply to you if I don't scroll on my phone?

04:47.630 --> 04:48.240
Fine.

04:51.870 --> 04:52.600
Well.

04:53.120 --> 04:54.040
Good night then.

04:57.810 --> 04:59.159
Good night.

05:07.280 --> 05:08.570
Goldthread...

05:08.590 --> 05:09.470
It has to be swapped.

05:09.500 --> 05:10.330
It's too bitter.

05:11.920 --> 05:13.680
Charred gardenia fruit.

05:13.680 --> 05:15.190
Looking so burnt and black,

05:15.190 --> 05:16.600
it can be removed for sure.

05:17.170 --> 05:18.190
And what else? Let me see.

05:27.800 --> 05:29.190
Ms. Shen, you're amazing.

05:29.680 --> 05:31.310
Can't believe you actually napped all the way until now.

05:31.720 --> 05:33.070
I'm back from school already.

05:34.190 --> 05:35.950
I woke up once,

05:35.950 --> 05:38.000
went to the bathroom and fell asleep again.

05:38.270 --> 05:39.270
Are you hungry?

05:39.430 --> 05:41.070
If you're hungry, let your dad heat the food for you.

05:41.070 --> 05:41.950
The dishes have gone cold.

05:43.450 --> 05:44.370
I have no appetite.

05:44.710 --> 05:46.230
I feel like I've slept for too long.

05:46.250 --> 05:47.250
I'm still groggy.

05:48.080 --> 05:49.790
I want to go downstairs for a walk.

05:49.820 --> 05:50.950
Do you two want to come with me?

05:51.390 --> 05:52.510
I can't go.

05:52.510 --> 05:53.830
I'm still grading papers.

05:54.430 --> 05:55.240
Mom.

05:57.530 --> 05:58.800
You want me to go with you?

05:59.680 --> 06:01.200
But the dating variety show I've been binge-watching

06:01.230 --> 06:02.640
just got updated today.

06:03.870 --> 06:04.990
Alright then.

06:05.010 --> 06:06.210
I'll go freshen up.

06:06.750 --> 06:07.190
Dad.

06:07.770 --> 06:09.240
Help me heat up the TCM liquid later.

06:09.400 --> 06:10.000
Okay.

06:10.110 --> 06:10.790
Okay.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.600
Does the medicine taste that bad?

06:40.470 --> 06:41.470
There's still some left.

06:41.510 --> 06:42.240
Take a sip, huh?

06:42.240 --> 06:43.159
Why would I?

06:43.159 --> 06:44.120
I don't have insomnia.

06:46.240 --> 06:47.360
Why are you out skateboarding

06:47.360 --> 06:48.240
at this hour today?

06:49.010 --> 06:50.010
I'm feeling groggy

06:50.040 --> 06:50.920
after a day's work.

06:51.240 --> 06:52.430
So I'm out to get some fresh air and unwind.

06:57.140 --> 06:57.890
What's that look?

06:58.390 --> 06:59.310
I can't skateboard?

06:59.700 --> 07:01.310
I think Tai Chi suits you better.

07:03.510 --> 07:04.430
Then, should I wear

07:04.430 --> 07:05.190
a traditional suit

07:05.190 --> 07:05.870
for Tai Chi?

07:05.870 --> 07:06.430
Yes.

07:06.430 --> 07:08.070
With a pair of plain cloth shoes.

07:10.190 --> 07:11.750
Are you really unbiased like you said?

07:12.390 --> 07:13.510
Do you think TCM physicians are all old men?

07:14.560 --> 07:17.000
They're always respectfully referred to as "Old TCM Physicians."

07:17.000 --> 07:19.430
If they're not old, why are they addressed as  "Old TCM Physicians?"

07:21.170 --> 07:22.650
You seem to be in good spirits today.

07:24.390 --> 07:26.020
I'm not mocking you.

07:26.570 --> 07:28.740
"Old" doesn't only refer to age.

07:28.770 --> 07:31.130
It's also about experience and professional capabilities.

07:31.510 --> 07:32.680
I'm complimenting you.

07:32.680 --> 07:33.830
After taking your medicine yesterday,

07:33.830 --> 07:35.360
I slept for four hours in the afternoon.

07:35.360 --> 07:36.040
It's very effective.

07:36.820 --> 07:37.740
Now we're talking.

07:41.560 --> 07:42.920
I'll go grab something at the convenience store ahead.

07:42.920 --> 07:43.510
Are you coming with me?

07:44.390 --> 07:44.830
Sure.

07:44.830 --> 07:45.650
I'll go buy some snacks.

07:45.680 --> 07:46.080
Let's go.

07:48.480 --> 07:49.550
What do you want to buy?

07:50.190 --> 07:50.870
I haven't decided yet.

07:50.870 --> 07:51.600
I'll just browse around.

07:52.750 --> 07:53.270
What about you?

07:53.770 --> 07:55.010
If I'm taking TCM medicine,

07:55.040 --> 07:56.190
can I drink cold Coke?

07:56.190 --> 07:57.240
Of course not.

07:57.240 --> 07:57.920
What about Sprite?

07:57.950 --> 07:58.550
No.

07:59.270 --> 08:01.870
Then can I eat spicy strips?

08:34.669 --> 08:36.000
Do you need anything else?

08:40.159 --> 08:40.909
I'll add on this too.

08:41.400 --> 08:42.039
Thank you.

08:46.440 --> 08:47.600
In total, it's...

08:48.340 --> 08:49.000
Just scan my payment code.

08:58.960 --> 08:59.720
Xifan.

08:59.790 --> 09:00.550
I bought this for you.

09:01.760 --> 09:02.920
Does it taste good?

09:02.940 --> 09:04.330
You drink this every time.

09:04.740 --> 09:05.980
It's really good!

09:06.010 --> 09:07.130
C'mon, give it a try.

09:09.630 --> 09:10.200
What's wrong?

09:16.230 --> 09:17.000
Nothing.

09:18.200 --> 09:19.000
Is it good?

09:20.360 --> 09:21.210
It's alright.

09:21.240 --> 09:22.430
I prefer the mint flavor.

09:30.450 --> 09:31.380
This is for you.

09:33.980 --> 09:35.270
Why are you giving me candies?

09:36.460 --> 09:37.980
Didn't you complain about TCM's bitterness?

09:38.240 --> 09:39.320
You can have a piece of mint candy

09:39.320 --> 09:40.550
each time you drink the medicine.

09:41.520 --> 09:42.710
The mint candy

09:42.740 --> 09:44.790
can help clear heat and detoxify.

09:45.250 --> 09:47.200
It won't mess with the medicine you're taking.

09:49.150 --> 09:49.750
Okay.

09:50.590 --> 09:51.400
Why are you smiling?

09:52.450 --> 09:54.940
I think you're too much of a workaholic.

09:55.270 --> 09:57.600
Even to give me some candies, you had to justify it with the TCM theory.

09:59.440 --> 10:00.240
What else should I say?

10:00.550 --> 10:01.840
"I'm giving you a pack of candies

10:01.840 --> 10:04.030
to wish you a sweet life?"

10:06.550 --> 10:09.000
It's better to wish my heat cleared

10:09.000 --> 10:10.790
and de... Detoxified?

10:12.780 --> 10:19.300
♫Continuous gloom, my failures, hard to let go♫

10:19.790 --> 10:28.370
♫But love comes with hurt; I'm a fool, never able to figure it out♫

10:25.000 --> 10:26.720
What's your building number?

10:27.360 --> 10:28.510
Building No. 2.

10:28.390 --> 10:35.420
♫Even if you don't give me an answer about the future♫

10:28.510 --> 10:29.270
Right here

10:30.240 --> 10:30.790
Alright.

10:31.670 --> 10:32.200
Well, then...

10:32.720 --> 10:33.320
Good night.

10:34.200 --> 10:34.720
Good night.

10:35.120 --> 10:36.030
Thank you for the mint candies.

10:36.090 --> 10:39.680
♫It became brighter because of you♫

10:36.670 --> 10:37.320
No problem.

10:38.030 --> 10:38.440
Bye.

10:39.030 --> 10:39.600
Bye.

10:39.800 --> 10:43.750
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

10:43.770 --> 10:47.490
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

10:47.510 --> 10:51.580
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

10:57.580 --> 11:01.010
[Staff Restaurant]

11:05.030 --> 11:06.000
He,

11:06.910 --> 11:08.780
what time are you going to the First People's Hospital this afternoon?

11:09.030 --> 11:10.190
Could you give me a ride?

11:10.720 --> 11:11.790
Why should I go there?

11:13.000 --> 11:13.880
Isn't your father,

11:13.960 --> 11:14.910
Professor He,

11:15.360 --> 11:16.670
going to hold a seminar there

11:16.670 --> 11:17.720
this afternoon?

11:17.860 --> 11:19.410
Are you not going with him?

11:20.440 --> 11:21.510
He's a doctor of Western medicine.

11:21.840 --> 11:23.050
Why would I go to a Western medicine seminar?

11:23.960 --> 11:24.770
Indeed...

11:28.550 --> 11:31.240
Professor He got transferred to North City two years ago, didn't he?

11:31.670 --> 11:32.360
During that time, did he...

11:32.380 --> 11:33.650
Do you have

11:33.960 --> 11:34.720
many appointments today?

11:35.550 --> 11:36.150
Yep.

11:36.660 --> 11:37.900
There are tons.

11:38.030 --> 11:39.300
That's why I'm here to eat so late.

11:39.600 --> 11:40.320
Then quickly grab a bite

11:40.320 --> 11:41.200
and get back to work.

11:41.200 --> 11:42.150
Yes, yes. I'm starving.

11:43.330 --> 11:45.490
Should quickly eat up and work.

11:47.270 --> 11:47.960
Senior He,

11:48.360 --> 11:48.910
the patient

11:48.910 --> 11:50.870
in bed number three just had surgery yesterday.

11:50.870 --> 11:51.910
Is he allowed to drink water today?

11:52.210 --> 11:53.570
Yes, keep a close eye on them.

12:00.740 --> 12:02.960
[He Sheng]

12:05.750 --> 12:06.510
I need to take this call.

12:06.790 --> 12:07.270
Sure.

12:13.530 --> 12:14.050
It's me.

12:15.170 --> 12:16.840
Uhm, are you busy this afternoon?

12:18.550 --> 12:19.360
Not really.

12:20.770 --> 12:23.080
I'm here in Hang City for an exchange event.

12:23.630 --> 12:25.150
I don't have any plans for tonight.

12:25.690 --> 12:26.850
I want to

12:27.170 --> 12:29.560
invite you and Li Jie's family out for dinner.

12:33.510 --> 12:34.510
I'm not available tonight.

12:37.850 --> 12:38.680
Okay.

12:39.960 --> 12:40.910
Next time then.

12:45.080 --> 12:45.770
You go ahead with your work.

13:39.690 --> 13:41.770
Mr. He Sheng, the famous cardiac surgeon,

13:41.800 --> 13:43.440
led a team of experts

13:43.460 --> 13:45.100
to our First People's Hospital today

13:45.150 --> 13:46.500
for an exchange activity.

13:46.520 --> 13:48.950
During this activity, Mr. He Sheng will

13:48.980 --> 13:51.550
have an in-depth discussion with the leaders and doctors

13:51.570 --> 13:53.120
from all major hospitals across our city

13:53.120 --> 13:54.910
on setting up new surgical departments

13:54.910 --> 13:56.630
and a fast mechanism of quick diagnosing

13:56.630 --> 13:58.000
and transferring patients,

13:58.000 --> 13:59.790
bringing convenience to the treatment of heart disease patients

13:59.790 --> 14:00.670
in our city.

14:01.440 --> 14:03.200
Now he remembers me after arriving in Hang City.

14:52.040 --> 14:52.840
Dr. He!

15:11.090 --> 15:13.260
♫Your face♫

15:14.150 --> 15:16.310
♫Right before my eyes♫

15:17.380 --> 15:20.480
♫Shining with radiant light♫

15:21.320 --> 15:25.560
♫Revealing all my thoughts♫

15:27.680 --> 15:29.680
♫So clearly♫

15:30.740 --> 15:32.970
♫Between us♫

15:34.070 --> 15:39.200
♫Each heartbeat becomes a prophecy♫

15:39.670 --> 15:42.970
♫Foreseeing the beginning of love♫

15:43.940 --> 15:47.930
♫I still miss it♫

15:48.110 --> 15:52.310
♫I'm starting to fall in love♫

15:50.720 --> 15:51.360
Dr. He,

15:51.790 --> 15:53.120
why aren't you using an umbrella?

15:52.330 --> 15:54.330
♫It's the light in your eyes♫

15:54.360 --> 15:56.360
♫Illuminating my world♫

15:56.390 --> 16:00.470
♫Warming my loneliness♫

15:56.750 --> 15:57.630
What are you waiting for?

15:57.630 --> 15:58.390
Hold it for me.

15:58.390 --> 15:58.960
You're too tall.

15:58.960 --> 15:59.790
I can't lift it high enough.

16:01.600 --> 16:02.390
Sorry.

16:04.950 --> 16:05.430
Well,

16:06.500 --> 16:07.660
let me send you back first.

16:07.690 --> 16:08.290
Okay.

16:26.270 --> 16:27.580
Did someone send you the flowers?

16:28.740 --> 16:29.310
You mean these?

16:30.440 --> 16:32.250
No, I bought them myself.

16:33.040 --> 16:35.640
I've been too busy to go to the florist lately,

16:36.040 --> 16:37.560
so I just went there to buy them.

16:38.240 --> 16:39.120
How's it?

16:39.140 --> 16:39.810
Looks good?

16:45.120 --> 16:45.790
Yes, pretty.

16:46.790 --> 16:47.550
Right?

16:48.030 --> 16:49.000
I also think so.

16:50.420 --> 16:53.120
♫So wonderful♫

16:53.790 --> 16:56.250
♫Your embrace♫

16:57.380 --> 17:02.470
♫The past and future no longer matter♫

17:02.810 --> 17:06.640
♫Staying in this moment is enough♫

17:06.990 --> 17:10.980
♫I still miss it♫

17:07.240 --> 17:08.290
Let me tell you,

17:09.040 --> 17:10.890
tulips of this colour

17:10.920 --> 17:12.030
are particularly hard to find.

17:11.220 --> 17:15.040
♫I'm starting to fall in love♫

17:12.530 --> 17:14.060
But I'm generous,

17:14.270 --> 17:15.160
so I'm giving you a bouquet of them.

17:15.060 --> 17:17.310
♫It's the light in your eyes♫

17:17.339 --> 17:19.339
♫Illuminating my world♫

17:17.790 --> 17:19.790
Since when do girls give boys flowers?

17:19.470 --> 17:23.530
♫Warming my loneliness♫

17:22.720 --> 17:25.200
As a patient,

17:23.950 --> 17:27.970
♫The understanding we've gathered♫

17:25.680 --> 17:28.590
I'm giving you this to express my gratitude to the doctor.

17:27.990 --> 17:31.720
♫Turns the pages of our future♫

17:29.030 --> 17:29.720
Take it.

17:30.780 --> 17:31.500
Thank you.

17:31.740 --> 17:33.740
♫Before we reach the end♫

17:33.820 --> 17:35.820
♫A long, drifting line remains♫

17:36.020 --> 17:39.790
♫Filled with thoughts of loving you♫

17:44.470 --> 17:45.270
I'm home.

17:45.290 --> 17:46.010
Bye!

17:46.330 --> 17:46.960
Your umbrella.

17:47.370 --> 17:48.200
It's okay.

17:48.310 --> 17:49.260
Keep it until my follow-up visit.

17:49.820 --> 17:50.450
Bye-bye.

18:17.540 --> 18:18.460
Dr. He.

18:18.810 --> 18:19.810
Why are you here at this hour?

18:19.840 --> 18:20.750
Where did you get these flowers?

18:20.920 --> 18:22.030
Someone gave them to me.

18:23.180 --> 18:24.500
Get me some herbs to take away.

18:24.980 --> 18:27.070
Wrinkled giant hyssop, magnolia.

18:27.090 --> 18:28.930
Are you making a sachet for someone again?

18:30.310 --> 18:30.880
Just a minute.

18:34.310 --> 18:35.590
Wrinkled giant hyssop...

19:06.070 --> 19:06.720
Here you go, Ms. Shen.

19:07.000 --> 19:07.880
Thanks.

19:17.520 --> 19:18.520
Remember to pay a follow-up visit.

19:21.960 --> 19:22.720
Okay.

19:23.550 --> 19:24.200
Copy that.

19:29.400 --> 19:30.160
Gosh!

19:31.400 --> 19:32.070
What's wrong?

19:32.350 --> 19:33.240
Look at this quickly.

19:33.240 --> 19:34.550
Someone posted a photo of a handsome guy in the residents' group chat.

19:34.550 --> 19:35.720
He's really hot!

19:35.880 --> 19:36.710
Come and take a look.

19:36.790 --> 19:37.590
Is he handsome?

19:39.070 --> 19:40.160
How old are you?

19:40.160 --> 19:40.830
His looks are stunning!

19:40.830 --> 19:42.160
Stop making a fuss.

19:42.160 --> 19:43.310
I'm obsessed with handsome guys out there

19:43.310 --> 19:44.640
as the man at home ain't attractive.

19:45.960 --> 19:46.880
Isn't he handsome?

19:47.880 --> 19:48.750
Look at the group chat.

19:48.750 --> 19:50.720
Zhang and Wang are all asking for his WeChat,

19:50.870 --> 19:52.460
wanting to arrange a blind date with their daughter.

19:53.030 --> 19:53.880
Our community group chat

19:53.880 --> 19:55.400
hasn't been this lively for a long time.

19:55.400 --> 19:56.510
Everyone's talking about it.

19:58.830 --> 19:59.830
He is pretty handsome

19:59.830 --> 20:00.790
and decently dressed.

20:00.790 --> 20:03.350
Isn't it the clinic you've been to for treatment?

20:06.310 --> 20:07.510
Yeah, that's right...

20:08.270 --> 20:10.070
It's the clinic where I got you the medicine.

20:10.440 --> 20:12.750
Look! I'm familiar with this background.

20:12.750 --> 20:13.720
And also, look at the drawer behind...

20:13.720 --> 20:14.920
I think so...

20:14.920 --> 20:15.830
Really?

20:16.350 --> 20:17.150
Give it to me.

20:18.270 --> 20:19.590
This clinic

20:19.590 --> 20:21.960
is near our neighborhood.

20:21.960 --> 20:23.830
My daughter went to see a doctor there.

20:24.400 --> 20:25.110
You even told them that?

20:25.110 --> 20:25.580
C'mon...

20:25.610 --> 20:26.960
Why not?

20:27.470 --> 20:28.350
Have you seen him before?

20:33.750 --> 20:34.590
You know him?

20:35.590 --> 20:36.510
I know him？

20:36.880 --> 20:37.680
See what he said!

20:37.680 --> 20:39.720
The security guard saw you two hanging out together.

20:42.990 --> 20:43.710
The security guard...

20:43.730 --> 20:45.650
He must have seen it wrong.

20:45.730 --> 20:47.580
There are so many people coming and going every day

20:47.610 --> 20:48.480
at our neighborhood entrance.

20:48.500 --> 20:49.700
It was not me, of course.

20:49.750 --> 20:50.640
I've got a common face.

20:50.640 --> 20:51.590
He mistook someone else for me.

20:58.750 --> 20:59.840
It's almost time.

20:59.860 --> 21:00.620
I'm going to see the doctor.

21:00.650 --> 21:01.410
Enjoy your meal.

21:01.430 --> 21:02.260
Okay.

21:18.110 --> 21:19.660
Miss Shen, are you going out?

21:31.600 --> 21:34.810
[Honganmen Clinic]

21:34.920 --> 21:37.750
[Registration Office]

21:50.980 --> 21:51.910
I know.

21:51.930 --> 21:52.850
But please get in line first.

21:52.880 --> 21:53.920
Otherwise, we can't let you

21:53.940 --> 21:54.590
see the doctor, right?

21:54.610 --> 21:55.810
Please hold on.

21:56.260 --> 21:56.980
Excuse me.

21:57.570 --> 21:58.330
Miss Shen,

21:58.670 --> 21:59.590
are you here for a follow-up visit?

22:00.570 --> 22:02.000
You're a little late today.

22:02.030 --> 22:03.600
Dr. He's appointments are fully booked till the afternoon.

22:03.940 --> 22:05.660
I don't think you can make it today

22:05.680 --> 22:06.610
as you came so late.

22:08.240 --> 22:09.030
Just a second.

22:10.730 --> 22:11.860
Come by around twelve.

22:12.140 --> 22:12.930
No need to book an appointment.

22:13.280 --> 22:14.330
Just knock on the door and come in.

22:16.270 --> 22:17.070
Okay.

22:19.470 --> 22:21.030
There's no need to book an appointment today.

22:21.130 --> 22:23.520
But why did it end up like this?

22:24.440 --> 22:25.550
They're not here to see the doctor.

22:26.040 --> 22:27.720
Dr. He was caught on camera yesterday

22:27.740 --> 22:29.460
when he came to the clinic without wearing a mask.

22:29.490 --> 22:31.240
The video is all over the place now.

22:31.260 --> 22:33.500
A security guard in the adjacent neighborhood has been spreading the word,

22:33.530 --> 22:35.140
saying that Dr. He works at our clinic.

22:35.360 --> 22:36.470
Oh, my God...

22:38.570 --> 22:40.680
Do you know why Dr. He always wears a mask?

22:41.450 --> 22:42.110
No.

22:42.110 --> 22:43.160
Because

22:43.160 --> 22:45.000
this has happened so many times before.

22:45.170 --> 22:47.040
The family members of some patients saw Dr. He's handsome face.

22:47.300 --> 22:48.210
They all tried to set him up with someone

22:48.240 --> 22:49.170
and arrange blind dates.

22:49.810 --> 22:51.040
We don't even dare to post his photo.

22:53.110 --> 22:53.720
Please wait here.

22:53.720 --> 22:54.350
I'll get back to work.

22:54.370 --> 22:55.020
Okay.

22:55.550 --> 22:56.030
Madam,

22:56.030 --> 22:56.880
excuse me...

22:56.880 --> 22:57.720
OK.

23:11.100 --> 23:11.690
Sir,

23:12.080 --> 23:14.120
what seems to be bothering you?

23:14.140 --> 23:16.620
Doctor, my daughter's been single for too long.

23:16.650 --> 23:18.890
I feel really uncomfortable.

23:19.360 --> 23:21.680
Doctor, look at my daughter. Please take a look.

23:23.200 --> 23:23.970
Please take a closer look.

23:24.000 --> 23:25.000
Good...

23:25.000 --> 23:25.350
Good, right?

23:25.350 --> 23:25.590
Yeah...

23:25.590 --> 23:26.920
P-Please take a closer look.

23:26.920 --> 23:28.480
I've seen it clearly. She's good.

23:28.500 --> 23:30.010
[TCM Clinic No. 3]

23:30.750 --> 23:31.510
Thank you.

23:31.700 --> 23:32.590
Here he comes, here he comes.

23:32.640 --> 23:34.240
It's him...

23:34.240 --> 23:35.400
Could you take off your mask?

23:35.400 --> 23:36.270
No need.

23:36.270 --> 23:38.400
You can tell his good genes

23:38.400 --> 23:39.790
just from his eyes and hair.

23:40.180 --> 23:42.530
Doctor, this is my daughter's resume.

23:42.560 --> 23:44.240
My genes are not that good, actually.

23:44.820 --> 23:46.180
I have genetic hair loss.

23:46.240 --> 23:48.270
Look, this is a wig!

23:48.270 --> 23:49.720
I have no hair if I take it off.

23:50.430 --> 23:51.360
Do you want to see it?

24:06.070 --> 24:06.880
Sirs and madams!

24:06.880 --> 24:08.070
it's twelve o'clock now.

24:08.070 --> 24:09.750
We don't start work until one in the afternoon.

24:09.980 --> 24:11.550
Let's go have lunch!

24:11.570 --> 24:13.570
Lin, Lin! Come and help!

24:13.600 --> 24:14.120
Madam!

24:14.400 --> 24:16.290
1 PM, yes, 1 PM.

24:16.320 --> 24:17.840
The doctors need to eat too.

24:18.110 --> 24:19.920
The doctors need to rest too.

24:20.100 --> 24:21.410
Come in the afternoon...

24:21.440 --> 24:21.960
We'll come in the afternoon.

24:21.980 --> 24:23.150
OK, see you this afternoon.

24:23.180 --> 24:23.750
1 PM, remember.

24:23.750 --> 24:24.880
The doctors need to rest too.

24:25.350 --> 24:26.350
We'll come in the afternoon.

24:26.510 --> 24:27.550
Goodbye...

24:27.550 --> 24:28.270
Okay...

24:35.120 --> 24:35.800
They've left.

24:37.410 --> 24:38.210
You can go now.

24:38.240 --> 24:38.680
Okay.

24:39.310 --> 24:39.720
Bye-bye.

25:08.440 --> 25:10.680
Dr. He, I'm at the entrance of the clinic.

25:11.030 --> 25:12.000
The nurse said

25:12.270 --> 25:13.230
you've stopped seeing patients?

25:14.460 --> 25:16.150
Ask Nurse Sun to bring you to the back door.

25:18.440 --> 25:18.930
Okay.

25:57.030 --> 25:57.720
Dr. He.

25:59.370 --> 25:59.890
Take a seat.

26:00.590 --> 26:01.200
Thank you.

26:08.440 --> 26:09.000
Oh, by the way,

26:09.330 --> 26:10.480
why are you here?

26:10.500 --> 26:11.350
Didn't you go for lunch?

26:12.750 --> 26:13.550
Not yet.

26:14.150 --> 26:15.940
There was a large crowd of people in the morning.

26:16.760 --> 26:18.760
Now I can finally get some fresh air in the backyard

26:20.200 --> 26:20.880
while

26:21.350 --> 26:21.880
waiting for you.

26:24.230 --> 26:25.790
Oh, sorry,

26:26.030 --> 26:27.640
If you haven't eaten,

26:27.640 --> 26:29.270
I just bought a sandwich.

26:29.680 --> 26:30.750
You can have it.

26:31.000 --> 26:31.750
Do you want some water?

26:31.750 --> 26:32.680
I can go buy you a bottle.

26:32.680 --> 26:34.070
Don't bother. The sandwich is enough.

26:34.790 --> 26:35.400
Thank you.

26:35.600 --> 26:36.280
You're welcome.

26:36.300 --> 26:37.170
I'll eat it later.

26:41.800 --> 26:44.750
Why did you go shopping so early in the morning?

26:45.080 --> 26:46.920
I failed to book an appointment in the morning.

26:47.000 --> 26:48.110
And I didn't wanna home either.

26:48.110 --> 26:49.400
So I went to watch a movie.

26:49.640 --> 26:51.540
It ended at 11:40.

26:51.640 --> 26:52.750
It took me 20 minutes to get here.

26:52.770 --> 26:54.100
It was exactly twelve o'clock when I arrived.

26:55.310 --> 26:56.750
If I had this time like you did,

26:56.750 --> 26:58.110
I'd go home for a nap.

26:58.710 --> 27:00.270
I don't wanna go home.

27:00.350 --> 27:02.550
Since my mom knew I came to see the doctor at your clinic,

27:02.550 --> 27:04.070
she kept asking me if I knew you.

27:04.920 --> 27:05.880
What did you say?

27:06.110 --> 27:07.620
I said I don't know you, of course.

27:08.070 --> 27:10.000
Otherwise, she'd definitely ask me for your WeChat.

27:10.000 --> 27:10.550
And then,

27:10.550 --> 27:11.830
everyone in my neighborhood

27:11.830 --> 27:13.110
will know your WeChat.

27:14.350 --> 27:15.310
That's horrifying.

27:15.550 --> 27:16.160
Right?

27:16.440 --> 27:17.110
Thank you.

27:17.230 --> 27:18.030
You're welcome.

27:24.680 --> 27:25.470
Dr. He.

27:26.000 --> 27:29.610
How do you feel about the mass match-making thing today?

27:30.690 --> 27:33.450
Don't even mention it. Today, I've finally come to realize

27:33.480 --> 27:35.610
how scary match-making and marriage pressure can be.

27:36.310 --> 27:38.070
Sometimes I feel like I'm a horse.

27:38.310 --> 27:39.000
People who buy horses

27:39.000 --> 27:41.640
need to check your quality,

27:41.640 --> 27:43.270
fur, and teeth.

27:44.160 --> 27:45.240
Sometimes

27:45.510 --> 27:46.720
I feel like I'm a chunk of pork

27:47.070 --> 27:48.310
being judged and picked by purchasers,

27:50.030 --> 27:51.270
yet no one thinks of me

27:51.270 --> 27:53.110
as a person with emotions and thoughts.

27:53.640 --> 27:54.550
Dr. He.

27:54.920 --> 27:56.240
May I ask

27:56.510 --> 27:57.960
how old you are?

27:58.440 --> 27:59.110
31.

27:59.750 --> 28:01.400
You're already 31,

28:01.800 --> 28:03.510
yet you didn't have such a feeling until now?

28:03.880 --> 28:05.750
Doesn't your family give you marriage pressure?

28:07.200 --> 28:08.720
My grandpa pushes me sometimes.

28:09.310 --> 28:11.160
But I was busy with work.

28:11.400 --> 28:13.880
So I didn't pay much attention to it.

28:21.400 --> 28:22.770
It's also possible

28:23.270 --> 28:25.400
that the right person

28:25.400 --> 28:26.430
hasn't appeared yet.

29:14.680 --> 29:15.310
Let's start.

29:22.960 --> 29:24.720
I'll close my eyes and take a rest.

29:29.920 --> 29:31.350
Is the IT Summit over?

29:31.670 --> 29:32.830
You're in a good mood now.

29:33.730 --> 29:34.490
Don't move.

29:36.030 --> 29:36.720
How did you know

29:36.720 --> 29:37.830
I was at the IT summit?

29:38.440 --> 29:39.590
I saw it on the news.

29:41.920 --> 29:43.240
I was on TV?

29:44.350 --> 29:46.960
I wonder if I looked good on camera.

29:49.940 --> 29:50.910
You looked pretty good.

29:52.000 --> 29:52.550
Okay.

29:53.000 --> 29:54.270
What do you work as in the hotel?

29:54.270 --> 29:56.240
I'm the manager of the Front Office.

29:56.560 --> 29:58.800
What does the manager of the Front Office do?

29:59.440 --> 30:01.160
Like, doing reception work in the lobby?

30:01.910 --> 30:04.020
No, The one you're talking about

30:04.040 --> 30:05.890
is the hotel lobby manager.

30:06.350 --> 30:08.110
Our job mainly includes

30:08.110 --> 30:09.960
checking room reservations,

30:10.110 --> 30:11.440
arranging rooms,

30:11.660 --> 30:13.900
and attending events and meetings

30:14.750 --> 30:16.960
during holidays

30:16.960 --> 30:18.550
with the Marketing Department.

30:18.830 --> 30:21.240
For example, we were pretty busy

30:21.950 --> 30:23.560
during the IT Summit this time.

30:23.750 --> 30:25.270
We needed to gather the participants

30:25.270 --> 30:27.030
in the same area

30:27.590 --> 30:29.880
for better service and management.

30:30.510 --> 30:31.200
Besides,

30:31.200 --> 30:33.790
we had plenty of other work to handle.

30:34.200 --> 30:35.550
Like

30:36.070 --> 30:38.830
changing their sheets and quilt covers

30:39.500 --> 30:41.740
or setting up the mini wine party they wanted

30:41.760 --> 30:43.410
in the room.

30:44.350 --> 30:45.960
So you know what?

30:46.920 --> 30:49.550
I've been swamped with work lately.

30:49.720 --> 30:50.640
I saw it.

30:51.440 --> 30:52.790
It was pretty tiring.

30:57.010 --> 31:03.320
♫You're like a gentle wind♫

31:03.770 --> 31:09.330
♫After early summer afternoon, it blows past my heart♫

31:10.630 --> 31:16.830
♫When your fingers touch my hands♫

31:17.560 --> 31:22.180
♫So you're also here for me♫

31:24.590 --> 31:30.180
♫I hear you say, red beans grow in the southern lands♫

31:31.160 --> 31:34.020
♫When spring comes, a few branches begin to sprout♫

31:34.550 --> 31:38.020
♫Cherish the youth♫

31:39.860 --> 31:45.780
♫Loving you is the best thing I've ever done♫

31:46.750 --> 31:51.630
♫Among the vast sea of people, you and I understand each other♫

31:53.480 --> 31:59.400
♫Missing you is the most beautiful thing in my life♫

32:00.340 --> 32:05.550
♫Write it down in your heart and never disappear♫

32:18.590 --> 32:19.160
Wake up.

32:33.110 --> 32:34.750
What's this scent?

32:34.750 --> 32:37.960
It's so good. I fell asleep after smelling it.

32:38.680 --> 32:39.790
You're sharp-nosed.

32:41.160 --> 32:41.550
Alright.

32:41.830 --> 32:42.880
put on your shoes and get up.

32:56.880 --> 32:58.440
Your sachet's scent must have worn off by now, huh?

32:59.110 --> 33:00.060
I made you a new one.

33:01.900 --> 33:02.620
Thank you.

33:03.940 --> 33:05.310
And the prescription is also done.

33:15.430 --> 33:16.230
Thanks.

33:27.140 --> 33:28.250
What's that look on your face?

33:29.510 --> 33:30.200
What's wrong?

33:30.470 --> 33:31.680
Are you afraid I'll poison you?

33:33.030 --> 33:33.680
Nope.

33:39.110 --> 33:40.020
Well, Dr. He,

33:40.320 --> 33:41.410
can we

33:41.440 --> 33:43.110
remove the goldthread?

33:44.250 --> 33:45.010
No.

33:45.110 --> 33:45.720
Fine.

33:46.000 --> 33:47.030
Then can we

33:47.030 --> 33:48.510
remove this charred gardenia?

33:49.510 --> 33:50.200
No.

33:50.200 --> 33:50.590
Alright.

33:50.960 --> 33:52.110
Can we...

33:52.110 --> 33:53.920
Are you questioning my medical skills?

33:55.560 --> 33:57.120
No, I didn't mean that.

34:02.640 --> 34:03.640
It's just...

34:04.070 --> 34:06.110
After taking the medicine,

34:06.110 --> 34:07.880
I did a quick research.

34:08.030 --> 34:11.230
I found that the goldthread and charred gardenia have the same medicinal properties.

34:11.230 --> 34:12.630
They both help clear heat and reduce dampness.

34:12.940 --> 34:14.900
It's unnecessary to have two sorts of herbs

34:14.929 --> 34:16.250
with the same medicinal properties

34:16.270 --> 34:17.909
in one prescription, right?

34:20.440 --> 34:22.920
You did a quick research?

34:23.889 --> 34:25.590
I think you're just afraid of extra expenses if I prescribe

34:25.590 --> 34:26.550
extra medicinal materials.

34:26.960 --> 34:27.590
No.

34:27.880 --> 34:28.710
So why?

34:31.440 --> 34:32.250
Dr. He,

34:33.190 --> 34:35.060
the medicine last time

34:35.580 --> 34:38.060
was way too bitter.

34:41.710 --> 34:42.760
Someone

34:42.900 --> 34:44.219
can endure either hardships at work

34:44.250 --> 34:46.199
or pain in life.

34:46.630 --> 34:49.510
Yet she can't bear to take a small pack of bitter herbal medicine.

34:49.570 --> 34:50.850
They're not the same.

34:50.880 --> 34:52.510
TCM offers real bitterness

34:52.510 --> 34:54.230
that I need to swallow.

34:55.010 --> 34:57.970
So you studied TCM to avoid

34:58.010 --> 34:59.340
this bit of bitterness?

34:59.900 --> 35:01.220
What a hardworking girl.

35:03.290 --> 35:04.080
Thank you.

35:06.440 --> 35:06.880
Tell me

35:07.040 --> 35:08.440
if there's anything else you wanna remove.

35:10.230 --> 35:10.960
No more.

35:10.960 --> 35:11.840
Are you sure?

35:26.240 --> 35:28.800
Dr. He, let me do you a favor.

35:29.110 --> 35:29.920
What?

35:33.820 --> 35:34.570
Check this out.

35:36.910 --> 35:37.980
Does it look like a ring?

35:41.840 --> 35:42.280
Gimme your hand.

35:46.750 --> 35:47.510
C'mon!

36:13.500 --> 36:14.580
Take it.

36:14.600 --> 36:15.480
You're welcome.

36:27.670 --> 36:28.920
Are you asking me to

36:29.440 --> 36:30.440
pretend to be married?

36:32.620 --> 36:34.190
This is all I can do to help you.

36:34.590 --> 36:35.400
As for the rest,

36:35.400 --> 36:36.590
it depends on your acting skills.

36:37.030 --> 36:37.960
Thank you for the medicine

36:37.960 --> 36:38.840
and your sachet.

36:39.360 --> 36:39.840
Bye.

36:41.550 --> 36:43.640
♫So clearly♫

36:44.550 --> 36:46.910
♫Between us♫

36:48.160 --> 36:53.020
♫Each heartbeat becomes a prophecy♫

36:53.610 --> 36:56.970
♫Foreseeing the beginning of love♫

36:59.830 --> 37:03.940
♫I still miss it♫

37:03.960 --> 37:07.870
♫I'm starting to fall in love♫

37:07.890 --> 37:10.170
♫It's the light in your eyes♫

37:10.190 --> 37:12.350
♫Illuminating my world♫

37:12.370 --> 37:15.970
♫Warming my loneliness♫

37:16.420 --> 37:20.380
♫The understanding we've gathered♫

37:20.410 --> 37:24.810
♫Turns the pages of our future♫

37:24.830 --> 37:26.830
♫Before we reach the end♫

37:26.670 --> 37:27.550
Auntie.

37:27.110 --> 37:28.860
♫A long, drifting line remains♫

37:27.570 --> 37:29.210
Are you feeling unwell somewhere?

37:29.070 --> 37:32.040
♫Filled with thoughts of loving you♫

37:38.570 --> 37:39.070
Wait a second.

37:39.400 --> 37:39.960
You...

37:42.000 --> 37:42.510
It's a wedding ring.

37:42.780 --> 37:43.780
You're already married?

37:44.320 --> 37:45.710
Then why are you looking at my daughter's information?

37:45.890 --> 37:46.960
I thought

37:46.990 --> 37:48.150
you wanted me to see

37:48.170 --> 37:49.040
her complexion.

37:49.060 --> 37:49.750
Auntie,

37:50.070 --> 37:51.360
your daughter's complexion

37:51.360 --> 37:52.630
shows that she has a deficiency in qi and blood.

37:53.950 --> 37:55.660
What's wrong with the people in the group?

37:55.680 --> 37:57.290
They didn't even bother to check the situation clearly.

37:57.840 --> 37:59.000
He's clearly already married.

37:59.000 --> 37:59.920
Seriously.

38:02.420 --> 38:04.750
Auntie, tell your daughter to make an appointment with me.

38:08.680 --> 38:09.880
Who posted this in the group?

38:09.910 --> 38:12.070
This doctor is already married. Who posted this?

38:12.100 --> 38:13.210
Isn't it just messing with us?

38:13.240 --> 38:14.390
Exactly, exactly.

38:14.520 --> 38:17.400
How unlucky. I thought this doctor was quite suitable.

38:34.340 --> 38:37.130
Dr. He, I have dinner plans with friends tonight.

38:37.160 --> 38:38.440
I won't have time to pick up the medicine.

38:39.040 --> 38:41.480
Could you please help me pick it up?

38:43.510 --> 38:44.070
Okay.

38:57.810 --> 39:00.000
Dr. He, I've arrived at the park near my home.

39:02.110 --> 39:02.920
Please enjoy your meal.

39:03.360 --> 39:04.000
Ms. Shen,

39:05.840 --> 39:06.920
come here.

39:06.920 --> 39:07.920
What a coincidence!

39:08.650 --> 39:09.700
Your dad just ordered.

39:11.830 --> 39:12.310
Come quickly.

39:14.220 --> 39:16.340
Change meeting location, change meeting location.

39:16.370 --> 39:17.290
Reply if you received.

39:17.390 --> 39:17.950
Fine.

39:18.410 --> 39:19.220
Give it to me.

39:19.920 --> 39:21.150
How did you end up here?

39:21.150 --> 39:21.800
Sit down quickly.

39:22.070 --> 39:22.920
The buns are still hot.

39:23.090 --> 39:24.610
How did you all end up here?

39:24.640 --> 39:27.200
Your dad insisted on eating buns today.

39:28.070 --> 39:29.400
I don't want to cook anymore.

39:30.710 --> 39:31.710
Have some vinegar.

39:32.000 --> 39:33.060
Okay.

39:33.080 --> 39:34.930
Is it okay if I pour your vinegar here?

39:35.000 --> 39:35.550
That's fine.

39:40.090 --> 39:40.930
It's pork.

39:43.190 --> 39:44.030
There's also some bamboo shoots inside.

39:45.070 --> 39:46.030
What are you doing?

39:46.030 --> 39:46.670
Mosquito.

39:47.280 --> 39:48.590
Why would there be mosquitoes this season?

39:48.590 --> 39:49.400
There are no mosquitoes.

39:50.070 --> 39:51.230
Stop messing around, stop it.

39:51.230 --> 39:51.800
Hurry up.

39:51.800 --> 39:52.800
Quickly, eat up.

39:52.800 --> 39:54.000
Don't fool around.

39:58.520 --> 39:59.250
Stop shaking it.

39:59.280 --> 40:00.550
You'll drop your phone again.

40:10.280 --> 40:11.360
Eat quickly.

40:15.730 --> 40:18.330
I suddenly got a message.

40:18.360 --> 40:19.110
The clinic is asking me

40:19.110 --> 40:20.670
to go pick up the medicine quickly.

40:20.670 --> 40:21.630
They're waiting for me.

40:21.890 --> 40:22.710
Don't go.

40:22.710 --> 40:23.880
I'll pick it up for you later, won't that do?

40:23.880 --> 40:24.400
No need, no need.

40:24.400 --> 40:25.110
I'm finished eating.

40:25.110 --> 40:26.070
I'll go over in a bit, okay?

40:26.070 --> 40:26.630
It's so late.

40:26.630 --> 40:28.070
Let your dad go with you.

40:28.120 --> 40:29.890
No need. My dad should stay with you.

40:29.920 --> 40:31.280
I can't break up the couple.

40:46.470 --> 40:47.280
Dr. He,

40:53.400 --> 40:54.920
you just scared me to death.

40:55.070 --> 40:55.590
What's wrong?

40:56.150 --> 40:58.800
You just appeared in front of my parents like that.

40:59.190 --> 41:00.760
Aren't you afraid they'll recognize you?

41:01.760 --> 41:02.510
What's wrong with that?

41:03.840 --> 41:04.960
What's the need to be so mysterious?

41:05.290 --> 41:06.930
If they recognize you,

41:06.960 --> 41:08.760
they'll definitely ask for your contact information.

41:09.230 --> 41:10.880
Then all the elderly in our neighborhood

41:10.880 --> 41:11.880
will have your WeChat.

41:13.280 --> 41:13.960
That's true.

41:14.430 --> 41:15.630
I forgot about that.

41:16.750 --> 41:17.350
Yes.

41:18.880 --> 41:20.110
Your medicine.

41:20.910 --> 41:22.150
Take it, it's a bit heavy.

41:22.400 --> 41:23.070
Be careful.

41:25.320 --> 41:25.760
Thank you.

41:27.230 --> 41:27.880
Um,

41:28.270 --> 41:29.800
this thing that you gave me at noon

41:30.600 --> 41:31.370
is gone.

41:31.400 --> 41:32.240
I lost it.

41:33.600 --> 41:35.330
It disappeared right when I got off work.

41:36.210 --> 41:36.850
How about

41:36.880 --> 41:37.760
I buy you another one?

41:38.150 --> 41:39.280
It's okay, no need.

41:39.280 --> 41:40.360
It wasn't expensive anyway.

41:40.530 --> 41:41.610
I'm glad it could help you.

41:42.350 --> 41:43.140
Okay.

41:44.690 --> 41:46.520
Well, I'm heading home then.

41:48.660 --> 41:49.340
Good night.

41:50.250 --> 41:50.880
Good night.

41:56.190 --> 41:56.920
By the way.

41:58.450 --> 41:59.450
Don't rush.

41:59.710 --> 42:00.790
Go in after a while.

42:00.810 --> 42:02.560
Don't let my parents see us together.

42:05.360 --> 42:05.800
Okay.

42:07.480 --> 42:08.030
Good night.

42:10.440 --> 42:10.960
Bye.

42:19.710 --> 42:20.870
Why so mysterious?
